imdb.plot outline: This is a YouTube Web-Series Traveling show Distributed by Fullscreen Media [US] featuring iAda aka GloomyMoonChild aka Ada Anane. "Come with me on my show as I travel the world in search of beauty, interesting culture, great tasting food, new fashion, and love." This is a Travel show where I take you YouTube video blogging Across as many family trips and trips with my friends as I can go on, please join me, you just have to kick back relax click that play button and enjoy.
